s-03,checkoutservice,frontend-2,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"LS4PSXUNUM\"\"\",出现次数:4\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"LS4PSXUNUM\"\"\",出现次数:4\naiops-k8s-03,checkoutservice,frontend-2,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"OLJCESPC7Z\"\"\",出现次数:4\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"0PUK6V6EV0\"\"\",出现次数:4\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"OLJCESPC7Z\"\"\",出现次数:4\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"LS4PSXUNUM\"\"\",出现次数:4\naiops-k8s-06,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"66VCHSJNUP\"\"\",出现次数:4\n", "matched_anomaly": "The system experienced an anomaly from 2025-06-26T18:10:05Z to 2025-06-26T18:26:05Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-26 18:10:05+00:00 to 2025-06-26 18:26:05+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "根据获取到的日志数据，我们可以识别出以下错误模式和异常组件：\n\n### 错误模式\n日志显示了多个有关 `frontend` 服务的 `rpc error`，错误信息为 `failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product #`，这表明 `frontend` 服务在尝试完成订单时遇到了内部错误，未能成功获取所需的产品信息。\n\n### 日志关键词提取\n- 错误类型：`rpc error`, `Internal`\n- 日志标签：`frontend--rpc error`\n- 异常名称：`InternalError`\n\n### 公共嫌疑人\n所有的错误日志都指向 `frontend` 服务作为发起错误请求的组件，但没有显示 `frontend` 服务之外的对其他服务或者特定原因的明显抱怨或者依赖性问题。\n\n### 分析结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"rpc error\", \"Internal\", \"frontend--rpc error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"The frontend service failed to complete orders due to 'rpc error' indicating internal errors when attempting to prepare orders.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"All gathered logs from the frontend service show a failure to prepare orders with messages indicating 'rpc error' and 'Internal desc = failed to prepare order'.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n当前的分析表明`frontend`服务在尝试准备订单时遇到了内部错误，但具体的根本原因尚不明确，可能需要更深入的日志或跨服务分析来识别潜在的依赖问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据获取的数据，我们分析了异常期间的指标变化，重点识别了服务层面的显著异常指标。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n### 异常指标识别\n1. **Checkout Service**：通过以下异常指标表现显著的变动：\n   - `error_ratio` - 中位数由0.0升到68.18，P99变化率为2.0\n   - `rrt` - 中位数由7230.24升到293051.56，P99变化率为1.9493\n   - `rrt_max` - 中位数由198163.5升到4348137.0，P99变化率为1.8991\n\n2. **Frontend Service**：展示了延迟和错误率的显著上升：\n   - `server_error_ratio` - 中位数由0.0升到最高0.31，变化略显显著，P99变化率为2.0\n   - `rrt_max` - 中位数从233270.5到3975290.5，变化率为1.7783，P99变化率为1.8563\n\n3. **Cart Service**：响应时间变化显著：\n   - `rrt_max` - 起幅变化，变化率为1.417\n   - `rrt` - 范围内微幅变化\n\n### 异常原因推测\n#### 检测到的异常原因：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error ratio and significantly increased response time (rrt) indicating potential service bottleneck or fault.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased to 68.18 and rrt increased to 293051.56.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased server error ratio and response time suggest possible frontend service overload.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio and rrt_max have increased concurrently.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated response times indicate service latency issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased within observed period.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此分析结果表明在指定时间段内，多个服务层面异常频发，尤其是 Checkout Service 和 Frontend Service 的表现异常突出，可能是资源瓶颈或某种配置错误导致的服务性能下降。具体根因尚需进一步 Log 和 Trace 数据补充确认。", "trace_analysis_findings": "分析已完成，以下是对 trace 数据的全面扫描结果和初步发现。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"deadline_exceeded\",\n    \"connection_refused\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著延迟并且报错：connection error on ProductCatalogService.GetProduct\",\n      \"evidence\": \"anomaly_avg_duration = 2614825.93ms 对比正常时段 19533.07ms，异常倍数 > 100。观察到 desc= 'transport: Error while dialing dial tcp'.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"多次调用 PlaceOrder 过程中，checkoutservice 的响应时间显著增加。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1 到 checkoutservice 的调用 latency = 3,458,065 ms 相较于正常时段的 153,703 ms，延迟提升 > 20 倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"购物车服务的 GetCart 接口延迟大幅增加，并对 redis 依赖的访问同样出现异常。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis 的读操作（HGET）在 peak 准点从正常 1,739ms 升至 79,511ms。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\n#### 关键数据摘要：\n1. **checkoutservice 调用 productcatalogservice 出现 massive_lag**：调用 ProductCatalogService 的耗时大增至正常的约 134 倍。\n2. **frontend 调用 checkoutservice 出现延迟传导现象**：CheckoutService 的调用异常导致 Frontend 等后续逻辑受影响。\n3. **Checkout 调用的 CartService 与 Redis 的深层问题**：Redis 出现不寻常的响应时间可能引发购物车的响应延迟。\n\n这些发现表明，延迟极有可能是多层调用链传播下游问题所导致。下一步建议深入分析。（例如焦点放在 ProductCatalog 重启情况、Redis内部健康状态排查）"}
